sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Client as Client App
    participant API as OpenKey API
    participant TEE
    participant Email as Email Service

    User->>API: Request export for key
    activate API
    API->>Email: Send export notification
    API-->>User: Require 2FA verification
    deactivate API

    User->>API: Email confirmation code
    activate API
    API-->>User: Email verified
    deactivate API

    User->>API: Passkey verification
    activate API
    API->>API: Start 24-hour timer
    API-->>User: Export request confirmed
    deactivate API

    Note over API,Email: 24-hour delay window<br/>User can cancel anytime

    API->>Email: Send reminder at T-4h
    Email-->>User: "Export will complete in 4 hours"

    Note over User,Client: After 24 hours elapsed

    User->>Client: Generate ephemeral X25519 keypair
    activate Client
    Client->>API: Execute export (with ephemeral public key)
    deactivate Client

    activate API
    API->>TEE: Unseal private key for export
    activate TEE
    TEE->>TEE: HPKE encrypt to recipient public key
    TEE-->>API: HPKE ciphertext
    deactivate TEE
    API-->>Client: Encrypted blob
    deactivate API

    activate Client
    Client->>Client: Decrypt with ephemeral private key
    Client-->>User: Display raw private key
    deactivate Client

    Note over User: Key is now exported<br/>User must securely store it
